{
  "stem": "1753.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 91.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For example, I related earlier that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I escaped the Lodz ghetto, and then I went into another ghetto, a smaller ghetto, that was just created that very day, about 20 kilometers from Lodz.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, the name of the town was Szczecin, near Lodz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then subsequently, I went to Kutno to board a train and to go to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And those trains were compartmented into three different areas, between Germans, ethnic Germans, [NON-ENGLISH] and Poles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I had to figure out which-- where would I go?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My Polish, having been born in Germany, was limited.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So but the Polacks would have loved nothing better but to grab a Jew and turn them over to the Nazis, even though the Nazis didn't like them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I wouldn't take any chance, so I figured my best chance to take that trip to Warsaw would go into the German car, where the German soldiers were on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sure enough, I wound up next to-- sitting between a couple of SS men.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they asked me, 'So hey, young man, where are you going?' Naturally, my German, is-- in those years in particular, was absolutely perfect.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I say, 'I'm going to Warsaw.' They said, 'What are you doing in Warsaw?' I said, 'My-- my father is head of the main railway station in Warsaw, The Hauptbahnhof in Warsaw.' Oh, wonderful.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Oh, good, good, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they gave me food, chocolate, all kinds of goodies, and apparently, it comes with you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was nervous, I wasn't sure of myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it takes a lot of guts.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
